{"tid":330281,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"怪獸特攝片討論","createTime":"2017-07-21T05:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T05:05:55.000Z","uid":77403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9acd2e3285bc6c2bf28e0bd53eec2e013b1e11","tid":330281,"uid":77403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人鍾意睇哥斯拉 卡美拉呢D特攝片<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/124924_596bab6220c58faf2f21af1c3936e2d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F124924_596bab6220c58faf2f21af1c3936e2d4.jpg&h=81cbf1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哥斯拉我個人黎講首推機械哥斯拉系列真係打得好勁不論係1993年個套定2002個套<br />\n<br />\n卡美拉就首推卡美拉3 邪神覺醒 空戰一段D特技真係好正 卡美拉一個要打曬伊莉絲同人類 傷痕纍纍最後仲要一個打曬成班加歐斯仲要堅持戰鬥真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}